      • start

        public void start(Album thisAlbum)
        Populates photoList and imageViewList with photos from this album, and then making imageviews with those photos and adding them to imageViewList. Also links the album to this controller.
        Overrides:
        start in class Controller

      • closeAlbum

        public void closeAlbum()
        This method is used when we are getting out of the view from inside the album. So after a log out, a back to album button press, or a quit. What this does is it resets the photosList, imageViewList, tilePane, and the selections, as well as any other album-specific fields.
